{
  "stem": "979.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So Alma always used to go there to pass the evening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And one Sunday, she comes back at 11 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were all in bed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She was in the other room, but in her private little room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Suddenly, she's screaming and screaming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We all wake up, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What was wrong with her?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The block leader immediately got up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she ran to the hospital with her, and brought her to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the next thing, she comes back-- she died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, we don't know whether she killed her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe she would-- because they had-- there's two reasons now-- from food poisoning-- why come she didn't die?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's another story that came out there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She didn't die.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Alma Rose died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she had the same food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and the other thing is not only that, that Alma was very-- I mean, OK.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very good friends and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they found out Alma, because she was famous, they decided that they are going to let her go and play for soldiers to get her out of this mess-- of this mess where she is.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She told her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was thinking why her and not me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe that's why she-- she poisoned her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We'll never know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this one girl that I know, [INAUDIBLE], she worked for the-- at the hospital with-- and her-- one who became her husband.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They send the autopsy in Auschwitz, and they say that she died from-- not from food poisoning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She didn't die from food poisoning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the thing is-- no from food poisoning, that she-- she didn't do it to herself or whatever-- something like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They will lie there too if they want to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, then the next day, oh, we were all so upset.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
